createEvent(uint256,uint256,uint256,stri.details: Creates a new RTA NFT event and deploys its associated TicketKiosk.

createEventForCreator(address,uint256,ui.details: Creates a new RTA NFT event for a specific creator and deploys its associated TicketKiosk. This version allows specifying the creator address, useful for wrapper contracts.

finalizeAndTransfer(uint256).details: Business logic function for transfer. Called by the EventManager to check conditions and transfer the NFT.

getAllTicketKiosks().details: Returns all TicketKiosk addresses and their corresponding event IDs.

getCreatorEvents(address).details: Returns the events created by a specific creator.

getEvent(uint256).details: Returns the full data struct for a given event. For other contracts to easily get event data.

getStandaloneContracts().details: Returns the addresses of the standalone contracts.

getTicketKiosk(uint256).details: Returns the TicketKiosk address for a specific event.

initialize(address,address,address,addre.details: Initializes the contract addresses after deployment

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setFinalized(uint256).details: Allows the authorized EventManager contract to finalize an event.

setMetadataURI(uint256,string).details: Allows the authorized EventManager contract to update the metadata URI. The EventManager is responsible for handling all permission logic (e.g., only creator or delegate).

setReservePrice(uint256,uint256).details: Allows the authorized EventManager contract to update the reserve price.

totalEvents().details: Returns the total number of events created.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
